{"data":[{"date":"07:20 23/07","title":"B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/bi-clb-my-cam-hoa-mu-con-mat-tru-cot-do-chan-thuong.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Valencia ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu, Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. H\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Man United bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u1ed7 cho Matteo Darmian.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Valencia v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9. HLV Jose Mourinho lo ng\u1ea1i r\u1eb1ng anh s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c khi M.U ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Leicester City t\u1edbi s\u00e2n nh\u00e0 trong khu\u00f4n kh\u1ed5 v\u00f2ng m\u1edf m\u00e0n Premier League v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 10 th\u00e1ng 8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"MU b\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Valencia-roi-san-do-chan-thuong.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>M.U g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t Valencia do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng, HLV Mourinho c\u00f2n \u0111\u1ea7y lo l\u1eafng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a M.U. Sau khi v\u1ea5t v\u1ea3 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 1-1 v\u1edbi Club America, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, d\u00f9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c hay d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, M.U \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng mang l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3m h\u1ee9ng d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu. Ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd l\u00e0 Alexis Sanchez m\u1edbi t\u1edbi M\u1ef9 t\u1eadp trung song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 xoay chuy\u1ec3n th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Qua nhieu bai toan hoc bua cho HLV Jose Mourinho truoc mua giai moi\" title=\"Qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0i to\u00e1n h\u00f3c b\u00faa cho HLV Jose Mourinho tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/MU-0-0-San-Jose-Earthquakes-Them-mot-tran-giao-huu-that-vong-cua-bay-Quy-do-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">HLV Mourinho nhi\u1ec1u lo l\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00f9a m\u1edbi</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi Sanchez r\u1eddi s\u00e2n ph\u00fat 65, th\u1ebf c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a M.U c\u0169ng y\u1ebfu h\u1eb3n \u0111i. Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7 90 ph\u00fat song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tung ra n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Tahith Chong, Mason Greenwood r\u1ed3i Angel Gomes&hellip; c\u0169ng l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSu\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat, M.U ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. Vi\u1ec7c h\u1ecd b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng d\u00f9 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u01b0ng l\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra tr\u00ean s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool-172-191802.html\">B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1529","checkdouble":"191813"},{"date":"07:51 23/07","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7: Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/3/18/diem-tin-bong-da-sang-ngay-237-tiet-lo-3-muc-tieu-cung-co-hang-thu-cua-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd trong ph\u1ea7n \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 tr\u00ean chuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 23/7.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>B\u1ecb CLB M\u1ef9 c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a, M.U c\u00f2n m\u1ea5t tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t do ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng. </strong>Man United ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. H\u1ecd c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn tin d\u1eef khi Antonio Valencia d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp ch\u00e2n v\u00e0 s\u1edbm r\u1eddi s\u00e2n gi\u1eefa ch\u1eebng.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7ng c\u1ed1 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a M.U. </strong>Manchester United \u0111ang t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Harry Maguire, Toby Alderweireld ho\u1eb7c Leonardo Bonucci. Nh\u1eefng trung v\u1ec7 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ni\u1ec1m tin v\u1edbi HLV Jose Mourinho v\u00e0 \u00f4ng quy\u1ebft mang v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7 kh\u1ee7ng cho Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf t\u1eeb gi\u1edd t\u1edbi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a m\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 237 Ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/18/Thuong-vu-MU-mua-Leonardo-Bonucci-co-dien-bien-moi-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Bonucci l\u00e0 1 trong 3 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a M.U</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nSao Man City ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. </strong>Aymeric Laporte ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. Trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y ghen t\u1ecb v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Les Bleus khi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tri\u1ec7u t\u1eadp.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 mang v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c danh hi\u1ec7u cho Liverpool.</strong> Liverpool \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Steve Nicol tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca. </strong>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" title=\"Yerry Mina cua Barca\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/13/sao-sang-world-cup-thua-nhan-co-the-bi-da-khoi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool. </strong>Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1edbi s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng Lovren, Van Dijk r\u1ed3i Klavan, Gomez cho m\u1ed9t su\u1ea5t \u1edf trung t\u00e2m h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng n\u1eb1m trong danh s\u00e1ch du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 c\u1ee7a Juventus.</strong> Nh\u1eefng ai tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1eefa Real Madrid vs Juventus s\u1ebd c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00fat th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. L\u00fd do n\u1eb1m \u1edf ch\u1ed7 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a Juve s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 v\u00ec \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ph\u00e9p sau khi d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1528","checkdouble":"191814"},{"date":"08:19 23/07","title":"T\u1ea1o k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup, HLV Croatia t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Zlatko Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng h\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng cao h\u01a1n 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u00e1 qu\u00e2n World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a Croatia</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hau-chung-ket-world-cup-2018-khi-nguoi-thang-va-ke-thua-deu-do-ra-duong-465-191335.html\" target=\"_blank\">Croatia l\u00e0m n\u00ean k\u1ef3 t\u00edch \u1edf World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u00e1 qu\u00e2n</span> v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed. Ki\u1ebfn tr\u00fac s\u01b0 vi\u1ebft n\u00ean c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u00e0 Luka Modric, l\u00e0 Ivan Raktitic v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ch\u00ednh HLV Zlatko Dalic.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n 52 tu\u1ed5i th\u1ef1c ch\u1ea5t ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n ch\u1eefa ch\u00e1y c\u1ee7a L\u0110B\u0110 Croatia c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y m\u1ed9t n\u0103m sau khi sa th\u1ea3i ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ec1n nhi\u1ec7m Ante Cacic v\u00ec th\u00e0nh t\u00edch b\u1ebft b\u00e1t \u1edf chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/tao-ky-tich-o-world-cup-hlv-croatia-tu-lam-gia-ban-than.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Dalic chia tay Croatia \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm nh\u1eefng th\u00e1ch th\u1ee9c m\u1edbi trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau \u0111\u00f3, ch\u00ednh m\u1ed9t Dalic v\u00f4 danh t\u1eeb th\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn HLV n\u00e0y (7 n\u0103m l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c Trung \u0110\u00f4ng) \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a Croatia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t m\u1ea1ch t\u1eadn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tranh c\u00fap v\u00e0ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Dalic \u00fap m\u1edf chuy\u1ec7n ra \u0111i, t\u1ef1 l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00fa \u00fd h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u sau m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 l\u1ecbch s\u1eed c\u00f9ng Croatia, Dalic gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00edt nh\u1ea5t L\u0110B\u0110 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 CLB Premier League nghi\u00eam t\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft. Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, \u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed9ng th\u00e1i l\u00e0m gi\u00e1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;C\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn hay kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i \u0111ang l\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. V\u1eady th\u00ec con s\u1ed1 5 tri\u1ec7u USD/n\u0103m d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u00f3 v\u1ebb t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i \u00edt \u1ecfi so v\u1edbi ch\u1ebf \u0111\u1ed9 l\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1ed5ng m\u00e0 HLV xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc th\u1ee9 nh\u00ec th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng.&rdquo;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean ti\u1ec1n b\u1ea1c quan tr\u1ecdng th\u1eadt nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, n\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c s\u1ed1 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i c\u00f2n hai n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Croatia v\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh n\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i t\u1eeb th\u00e1ng Ba r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 l\u00fac n\u00e0o.&rdquo; &ndash; Dalic b\u1ecf ng\u1ecf chuy\u1ec7n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/17/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/bai-hoc-tu-nguoi-croatia-dat-nuoc-nho-giac-mo-lon-421-191456.html\">B\u00e0i h\u1ecdc t\u1eeb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia: \u0110\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1ecf, gi\u1ea5c m\u01a1 l\u1edbn</span><br>\r\n&ldquo;Mala zemlja, veliki snovi&rdquo; &ndash; D\u00f2ng ch\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ebft tr\u00ean xe bus ch\u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n qu\u1ed1c gia rong ru\u1ed5i c\u1ea3 th\u00e1ng h\u00e8 qua tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga. D\u1ecbch ra ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t:...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1527","checkdouble":"191815"},{"date":"08:16 23/07","title":"Mourinho b\u00e0o ch\u1eefa th\u1ebf n\u00e0o sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a th\u1ee9 2 t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t M\u1ef9.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nM.U b\u1ecb SJ Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb Club America c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 1-1, Man United l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc San Jose Earthquakes. S\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 th\u01b0a th\u1edbt t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Levi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ef1 b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ef1c t\u1ebf l\u00e0 M.U d\u00f9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn, Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf ch\u1ec9 tung ra c\u00f3 \u0111\u00fang 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch, \u00edt h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi SJ Earthquakes.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jose Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn MU 0-0 SJ Earthquakes h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/Jose-Mourinho-phat-bieu-sau-tran-MU-0-0-SJ-Earthquakes-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Sanchez kh\u00f4ng gi\u00fap M.U th\u1eafng SJ Earthquakes</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c M.U h\u00f2a kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u00e2y b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd cho nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00ednh c\u1ea3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t v\u1edbi Club America, vi\u1ec7c th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Mourinho li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u00f3 2 tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a khi \u0111\u00e1 giao h\u1eefu t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nMourinho kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes. \u00d4ng kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n kh\u00f4ng nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eadp n\u1eefa&rdquo;, Mourinho n\u00f3i v\u1edbi k\u00eanh MUTV. &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 g\u1eafn k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u00f3m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1eeb nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00e1c nhau. M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i 1, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 U23, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u1ec1 ho\u1eb7c m\u1edbi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i khi cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 c\u00f2n d\u01b0\u1edbi 18 tu\u1ed5i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mourinho tai My\" title=\"Mourinho tai My\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mourinho-bao-chua-the-nao-sau-tran-hoa-thu-2-tai-my.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Mourinho ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn M.U 0-0 SJ Earthquakes</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nAlexis Sanchez v\u00e0 Andreas Pereira l\u00e0 2 c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n c\u1ea3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc SJ Earthquakes. V\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen t\u1eeb th\u1ea7y Mourinho. &ldquo;Sanchez \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t&rdquo;, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i th\u00eam. &ldquo;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i cho \u0111\u1ed9i sau m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp ri\u00eang. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft v\u00e0 n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c, th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Sanchez c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1ng khen.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Pereira c\u0169ng \u1ed5n, t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n h\u01a1n nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n. Nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 c\u00e1 t\u00ednh, mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Man United tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/video-tong-hop-mu-00-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-326-191811.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes (Giao h\u1eefu h\u00e8 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu-172-191806.html\">Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\">MU 0-0 San Jose Earthquakes: Th\u00eam m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a b\u1ea7y Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-mu-lo-so-bi-cac-tai-nang-tre-dan-em-cuop-cho-172-191775.html\">Sao MU lo s\u1ee3 b\u1ecb c\u00e1c t\u00e0i n\u0103ng tr\u1ebb \u0111\u00e0n em c\u01b0\u1edbp ch\u1ed7</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00dd An (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1526","checkdouble":"191817"},{"date":"08:49 23/07","title":"MU l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a b\u1ea1c nh\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i v\u00e0 gia nh\u1eadp m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng l\u1edbn Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u kh\u00e1c m\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Khi Romelu Lukaku v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i sau k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n B\u1ec9, Anthony Martial \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed trung phong m\u0169i nh\u1ecdn, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec anh \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p HLV Jose Mourinho ch\u1ec9 g\u00f3i g\u1ecdn trong s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/23/mu-lai-gay-that-vong-mourinho-canh-bao-martial.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Mourinho c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a MU 0-0 San Jose</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn h\u00e0ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng Man Utd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ebf t\u1eafc, ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-bong-da/mu-vs-san-jose-earthquakes-giao-huu-he-2018-372-191798.html\" target=\"_blank\">CLB M\u1ef9 San Jose Earthquakes c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a 0-0</span>. \u0110\u00e2y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0110\u1ecf \u1edf IC Cup 2018, gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u giao h\u1eefu th\u01b0\u1eddng ni\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea1i M\u1ef9.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Mourinho \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng c\u1ea3nh b\u00e1o Martial nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i v\u1edbi \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ed9ng t\u1ed1ng c\u1ed5 anh ra kh\u1ecfi Old Trafford. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 mong mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i nh\u1eb1m c\u1ee9u v\u00e3n s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p, v\u1eady n\u00ean Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1eb7c Bi\u1ec7t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m giam c\u1ea7m c\u1eadu h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cC\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u1ee9 mu\u1ed1n g\u00ec l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ea5y. Nh\u01b0 t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y n\u00e0y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ea3 5 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Los Angeles, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i di chuy\u1ec3n hay thay \u0111\u1ed5i kh\u00e1ch s\u1ea1n v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u1ee9 th\u1ebf tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 Manchester chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi. Nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng, gi\u1edd t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf San Jose v\u00e0 sau \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Premier League v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i th\u1ee9 s\u00e1u.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, Martial \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u0103m tia nghi\u00eam t\u00fac b\u1edfi Chelsea v\u00e0 Tottenham. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p, Man Utd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn kh\u00f4ng \u201cn\u1ed1i gi\u00e1o cho gi\u1eb7c\u201d trong l\u00f2ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh v\u00e0 b\u00e1n anh cho Bayern Munich.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"mediaplayercontent\" data-href=\"https://video.bongda24h.vn/medias/MP4/2018/7/23/MU-1-0-San-Jose.mp4\" data-width=\"480\" data-height=\"320\" data-type=\"m4v\"><img src=\"/Images/video-chi-tiet.jpg\" style=\"width: 300px; height:220px\" alt=\"\"></div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1525","checkdouble":"191818"},{"date":"08:53 23/07","title":"HLV Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o, HLV Toshiya Miura \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa CLB TP.HCM v\u00e0 Than Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i ng\u00e0y 22/7, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng S\u00e0i th\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1 chung cu\u1ed9c nh\u1edd c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a ngo\u1ea1i binh Matias Gonzalez. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Miura \u0111\u00e3 b\u1edbt ph\u1ea7n lung linh khi h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn m\u1ed9t th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf v\u00ec l\u1ed7i v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o. \u0110\u00e2y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 hai trong m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i kh\u1ecfi s\u00e2n.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><em><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Toshiya Miura n\u00f3i g\u00ec khi h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 b\u1ecb \u0111u\u1ed5i v\u00ec thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u00f4 b\u1ea1o h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/24/hlv-miura-noi-gi-khi-chung-kien-hoc-tro-da-tho-bao.jpg\" /></em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Toshiya Miura l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 sau t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 pha v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c, HLV Miura \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan s\u00e1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3 n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c. Nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i, S\u1ea7m Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00f9 nh\u1eadn nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ebb. Sau pha b\u00f3ng, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng, ch\u01b0a chia s\u1ebb \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0110\u1ee9c.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>Trong k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, t\u00f4i mong Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c tinh th\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn v\u00e0 t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn h\u01a1n v\u1edbi anh ta\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a HLV Miura cho th\u1ea5y nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng b\u1ea3o v\u1ec7 h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng x\u1ea5u x\u00ed,\u00a0\u0111\u00e1ng l\u00ean \u00e1n c\u1ee7a h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 mang \u00e1o s\u1ed1 7.\u00a0<o:p></o:p>V\u1edbi t\u1ea5m th\u1ebb ph\u1ea1t n\u00e0y, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Ng\u1ecdc \u0110\u1ee9c s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i treo gi\u00f2 v\u00e0i tr\u1eadn t\u1ea1i V-League. \u0110\u00e2y ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1ed5n th\u1ea5t l\u1edbn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Th\u1ed1ng Nh\u1ea5t khi m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111ang c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh, HLV Miura cho hay: \u00a0\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 ph\u1ea3i th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 CLB ph\u1ea3i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecf. Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba qua th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, n\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3. V\u1edbi tinh th\u1ea7n v\u00e0 th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 t\u00edch c\u1ef1c nh\u01b0 hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd tr\u1edf n\u00ean t\u1ef1 tin h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o 6 tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cK\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u1edbi, h\u1ecd ch\u01b0a th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian ho\u00e0 nh\u1eadp. Nh\u01b0 Quang Huy ho\u1eb7c Marclei Santos ch\u1eb3ng h\u1ea1n. Kesley th\u00ec t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00ec anh ta bi\u1ebft r\u00f5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t. D\u00f9 sao \u0111i n\u1eefa, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 qu\u00e3ng ngh\u0129 ASIAD \u0111\u1ec3 \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt\u201d, \u00f4ng Miura ch\u1ed1t l\u1ea1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">CLB TP.HCM l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u01a1n l\u00ean v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 11 v\u1edbi 21 \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed9i cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C\u1ea7n Th\u01a1 t\u1edbi 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m.<br />\r\n<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-bong-da/tran-dau/tphcm-vs-quang-ninh-vong-20-vleague-2018-372-191786.html\">TPHCM 2-1 Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh (KT): V\u01b0\u1ee3t kh\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 HLV Miura l\u1ea1i tho\u00e1t kh\u1ecfi nh\u00f3m nguy hi\u1ec3m</span><br />\r\nC\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u1ee7a Matias Jadue gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a HLV Toshiya Miura th\u1eafng 2-1 khi ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u00f3n Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh \u1edf v\u00f2ng 20 gi\u1ea3i Nuti Caf\u00e9 V-League 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1524","checkdouble":"191820"},{"date":"22:37 22/07","title":"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Trung v\u1ec7 Joel Matip kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh \u0111\u00e3 s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn kh\u1ed1c li\u1ec7t cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m sau.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Matip tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Cameroon \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n v\u00e0 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00e8 n\u00e0y khi \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 giai \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng b\u1eafp \u0111\u00f9i. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, Matip bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i theo d\u00f5i The Kop thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn Lovren v\u00e0 Van Dijk t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh m\u1ed9t c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 \u0103n \u00fd.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nVi\u1ec7c thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u0169ng gi\u00fap cho Lovren c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool m\u00f9a sau. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Anfield h\u1ed9i qu\u00e2n c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o 6/8 t\u1edbi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i th\u00eam. Anh nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t trong nh\u1eefng tu\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf Premier League.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Matip s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u1edf Liverpool</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1edd v\u1eady, Matip s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Joe Gomez v\u00e0 Ragnar Klavan cho v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p c\u00f9ng Van Dijk. V\u00e0 c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Schalke t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cD\u0129 nhi\u00ean l\u00e0 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 c\u1ea1nh tranh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 t\u1ef1 tin. V\u00e0 t\u00f4i c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3 nghi ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 tin c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. V\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i, s\u1ebd c\u00f3 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng t\u1ed1i \u0111a c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c trao.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng tr\u00ean con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i. Th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ee7 100% nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 duy nh\u1ea5t c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n. Nh\u01b0ng s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb b\u00e2y gi\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea1t t\u1edbi n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t. T\u00f4i \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u00fang h\u01b0\u1edbng v\u00e0 c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y t\u1ef1 tin. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian n\u1eefa\u201d.</em></div>\r\n<h2>Matip tin v\u00e0o kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ea1nh tranh c\u1ee7a Liverpool</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Liverpool h\u00e8 n\u00e0y. The Kop li\u00ean t\u1ee5c chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng c\u00e1i t\u00ean ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 Naby Keita, Fabinho, Alisson Becker c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Shaqiri.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1eb7t ra nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u th\u1ee9. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd xem m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u ra sao nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng ngay t\u1eeb l\u00fac b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111i\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i t\u1ed1t\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Liverpool:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu-172-191769.html\">Klopp: MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1523","checkdouble":"191801"},{"date":"23:59 22/07","title":"B\u1ecb ch\u00ea mua Alisson v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 \u0111\u1eaft, Jurgen Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho... Man Utd","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong t\u1ea7m ng\u1eafm c\u1ee7a Liverpool.</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Pulisic<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chi 174 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho b\u1ed1n c\u00e1i t\u00ean g\u1ed3m Alisson (66.8), Naby Keita (52.75), Fabinho (43), Shaqiri (13.5), Liverpool c\u00f3 v\u1ebb nh\u01b0 ch\u01b0a mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i. Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool trong th\u1eddi gian t\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 Christian Pulisic c\u1ee7a Dortmund.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Jurgen Klopp ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Liverpool h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/22/jurgen-klopp-tiet-lo-muc-tieu-chuyen-nhuong-cua-liverpool.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Jurgen Klopp mu\u1ed1n Liverpool mua Christian Pulisic.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u00edch th\u00e2n HLV Jurgen Klopp kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"T\u00f4i th\u00edch Pulisic, t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1eeb khi c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ee9a tr\u1ebb. Pulisic ch\u01b0a nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n \u1edf M\u1ef9 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c. N\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y mu\u1ed1n t\u1edbi Anh ho\u1eb7c b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u01b0ng Pulisic \u0111ang \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u00e2u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t cho s\u1ef1 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n v\u00e0o l\u00fac n\u00e0y. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 14 \u0111\u1ebfn 15 n\u0103m trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng gian ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n. C\u00f2n vi\u1ec7c c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 t\u1edbi Liverpool kh\u00f4ng \u00e0? T\u00f4i ch\u1ecbu\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Jurgen Klopp th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 Pulisic v\u1eabn c\u00f2n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Dortmund. Ngo\u00e0i ra, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 19 tu\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1eddi M\u1ef9 hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 quan t\u00e2m c\u1ee7a Chelsea.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 t\u1ed9i cho MU<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Hai n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, Jurgen Klopp t\u1eebng ch\u00ea tr\u00e1ch Manchester United ph\u00e1 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00ec Paul Pogba v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 100 tri\u1ec7u euro. Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, The Kop l\u1ea1i bi\u1ebfn Alisson th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn Klopp h\u00e1 mi\u1ec7ng m\u1eafc quai.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Alisson\" title=\"Alisson\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/20/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson.jpeg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Alisson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi khi \u0111\u1ebfn Liverpool.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 bi\u1ec7n minh cho vi\u1ec7c ph\u00e1 k\u00e9t chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Alisson, Klopp \u0111\u1ed5 th\u1eeba cho Man Utd: \"\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i. Nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u1ebft ti\u1ec7t b\u1ea1n n\u00f3i, ch\u1eb3ng ai qu\u00ean. Nh\u01b0ng m\u1eb7t kh\u00e1c, \u0111\u00f3 v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt. T\u00f4i l\u00e0m sao c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i nhanh nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng hai n\u0103m r\u01b0\u1ee1i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"\"M\u1ed9t tr\u0103m tri\u1ec7u th\u1eadt l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3n ti\u1ec1n \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3. K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3, th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi thay \u0111\u1ed5i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1eaft nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng quan t\u00e2m th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi n\u00f3i g\u00ec, c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 Man Utd t\u1eebng b\u1ecf ngo\u00e0i tai nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u00e8 2018 c\u1ee7a Liverpool:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/mu-khong-co-kha-nang-chieu-mo-gareth-bale-vi-tien-luong-172-191761.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! L\u00fd do ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n MU chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Gareth Bale?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/100-nhm-liverpool-deu-muon-nghe-tin-nay-tu-klopp-172-191760.html\">100% NHM Liverpool \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n nghe tin n\u00e0y t\u1eeb Klopp?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings-172-191735.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-luon-tuong-tuong-minh-se-tro-thanh-gerrard-172-191724.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Gerrard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/liverpool-chanh-noi-khong-voi-nha-vo-dich-world-cup-172-191696.html\">Liverpool ch\u1ea3nh, n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1522","checkdouble":"191802"},{"date":"23:29 22/07","title":"HLV Tuchel gi\u1ee5c Rabiot quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/10/8/hlv-tuchel-giuc-rabiot-quyet-dinh-tuong-lai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid nh\u1eafm Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Khi m\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe b\u1ecb h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao th\u00ec Hazard tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 thi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chelsea-muon-mua-Anthony-Martial-thay-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real c\u00f3 Hazard l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Eden Hazard</span>, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mbappe (165 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (sau Neymar).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Real \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Hazard, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u euro) mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Martial th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Martial th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a CLB Bayer Leverkusen c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song The Blues ch\u1ec9 mua ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bundesliga trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Martial.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1521","checkdouble":"191803"},{"date":"02:22 23/07","title":"C\u1ee5c s\u1ed1c: Mesut Ozil b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/cuc-soc-mesut-ozil-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-dt-duc.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">S\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn d\u00e0nh cho Mesut Ozil</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Nh\u1eefng tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u1ee7a C\u1ed7 xe t\u0103ng b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mesut Ozil. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed sau tr\u1eadn thua 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ed9t c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean c\u00f2n lao xu\u1ed1ng s\u00e2n \u0111\u00f2i \u0103n thua \u0111\u1ee7 v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Ph\u00e1o th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u1ef1c s\u1ed1c Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c  h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/29/Cuc-soc-Mesut-Ozil-chia-tay-DT-Duc--hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ozil g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc, Ozil ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 t\u00e2m \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 g\u1eb7p \u00e1p l\u1ef1c b\u1edfi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tr\u00ean s\u00e2n c\u1ecf, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1988 c\u00f2n b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch khi ch\u1ee5p \u1ea3nh c\u00f9ng T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3, Recep Tayyip Erdogan.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong th\u1eddi gian v\u1eeba qua, Ozil \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu m\u1ed9t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p qu\u00e1 l\u1edbn. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra m\u1ed9t quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mesut Ozil chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c sau khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u00e1p l\u1ef1c, ng\u00f4i sao 30 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00e3 suy ngh\u0129 r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u01b0a ra quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110TQG, Ozil kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Buc anh day that vong cua Mesut Ozil\" title=\"B\u1ee9c \u1ea3nh \u0111\u1ea7y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Mesut Ozil\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/cuc-soc-mesut-ozil-bat-ngo-tuyen-bo-chia-tay-dt-duc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Mesut Ozil tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 chia tay \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i b\u1ecb mi\u1ec7t th\u1ecb ph\u1ea3i lu\u00f4n ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd thi\u1ebfu t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, sau t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec di\u1ec5n ra th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb gi\u00e3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi kho\u00e1c l\u00ean m\u00ecnh chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o c\u1ee7a \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng gi\u00e0nh r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u danh hi\u1ec7u, nh\u01b0ng b\u00e2y gi\u1edd t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac n\u1eefa. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi c\u00e1i c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 L\u0110B\u0110 \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed1i x\u1eed v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cH\u1ecd qu\u00ean r\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2009. H\u1ecd \u00edch k\u1ef7, bi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 tuy\u00ean truy\u1ec1n ch\u00ednh tr\u1ecb. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111\u00e3 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac t\u00f4i n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110TQG\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMesut Ozil \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 92 tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ea5u trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110T \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 23 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. Anh c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho Die Mannschaft v\u00e0o n\u0103m 2009. C\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y 4 n\u0103m, Ozil l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 \u0111\u00f3ng g\u00f3p n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt gi\u00fap \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/hlv-emery-thiet-chat-ky-luat-ozil-hoi-quan-som-cung-arsenal-172-191732.html\" target=\"_blank\">Ozil \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eadp trung tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i c\u00f9ng Arsenal</span>, anh c\u00f9ng c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1edbi Singapore \u0111\u1ec3 tham d\u1ef1 chuy\u1ebfn du \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf H\u00e8 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1520","checkdouble":"191804"},{"date":"02:37 23/07","title":"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2017/6/1/mateo-kovacic-yeu-cau-duoc-roi-real-madrid.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mateo Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018. Theo \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994 mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid c\u1eadp b\u1ebfn Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/2/Mateo-Kovacic-roi-Real-Madrid-cap-ben-Ngoai-hang-Anh-o-He-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u00a0Kovacic quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Real Madrid</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng khi th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n. T\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra \u0111i, n\u1ebfu nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb h\u1ee3p l\u00fd t\u00f4i s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng r\u1eddi Bernabeu\u201d.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHLV Lopetegui sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n gi\u1eef ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u1edf l\u1ea1i, \u00f4ng n\u00e0y t\u1ef1 tin s\u1ebd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c Kovacic ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi Real Madrid.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 v\u1eabn quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ra \u0111i. Theo Marca, Mateo Kovacic r\u1eddi Real Madrid \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ef1c cao, ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i l\u1ea1i l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Bernabeu. C\u1ef1u sao Inter \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1eb7p BL\u0110 Los Blancos \u0111\u00f2i ra \u0111i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Bi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00f4ng tin Kovacic mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Real Madrid, r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1994. \u1ede Anh c\u00f3 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn mu\u1ed1n s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ef1u sao Inter Milan, bao g\u1ed3m hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh Manchester v\u00e0 Tottenham.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Sao kh\u1ee7ng Croatia mu\u1ed1n d\u1ee9t t\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Real Madrid h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/3/7/Sao-khung-Croatia-muon-dut-tinh-voi-Real-Madrid-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn \u1edf Anh mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Kovacic</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-tbn/real-madrid-het-gia-khong-tuong-cho-mateo-kovacic-180-191234.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u00f2i 80 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Kovacic</span>, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n kh\u00f4ng t\u01b0\u1edfng cho m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb. Vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb Los Blancos l\u00e0m kh\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng, anh \u0111ang quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1eddi Bernabeu b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Kovacic li\u00ean t\u1ee5c tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 ra \u0111i, Real Madrid nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef anh \u1edf l\u1ea1i. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia T\u00e2y Ban Nha c\u0169ng bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3m gi\u00e1 b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u0169ng theo Marca, v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 thu v\u1ec1 kho\u1ea3ng 40 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng t\u1eeb Kovacic, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chi ra \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a ng\u00f4i sao 24 tu\u1ed5i r\u1eddi Bernabeu.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede Italia, Juventus v\u00e0 Napoli c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 quan t\u00e2m Kovacic, song c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia \u01b0u ti\u00ean chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Anh n\u1ebfu r\u1eddi Real Madrid. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 24 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eed s\u1ee9c \u1edf m\u00f4i tr\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ea7y kh\u1eafc nghi\u1ec7t nh\u01b0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)\u2003</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1519","checkdouble":"191805"},{"date":"02:59 23/07","title":"Chelsea \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao kh\u1ee7ng MU","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/21/chelsea-dam-phan-chieu-mo-sao-khung-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef Eden Hazard</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nReal Madrid nh\u1eafm Eden Hazard nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3 \u1edf k\u1ef3 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng H\u00e8 2018, vi\u1ec7c Ronaldo ra \u0111i bu\u1ed9c Los Blancos ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 thay th\u1ebf. Khi m\u00e0 Neymar v\u00e0 Mbappe b\u1ecb h\u00e9t gi\u00e1 qu\u00e1 cao th\u00ec Hazard tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u00e1i t\u00ean kh\u1ea3 thi nh\u1ea5t.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial thay Eden Hazard h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/18/Chelsea-muon-mua-Anthony-Martial-thay-Eden-Hazard-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Real mu\u1ed1n mua b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Eden Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Real c\u00f3 Hazard l\u00e0 c\u1ef1c cao khi m\u00e0 \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n kho\u00e1c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Bernabeu, ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 c\u0169ng kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 r\u1eddi Chelsea sau 6 n\u0103m g\u1eafn b\u00f3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u00e1o ch\u00ed Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-anh/cuc-nong-chelsea-dong-y-ban-hazard-cho-real-voi-so-tien-sieu-khung-172-191665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Real \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn mua Eden Hazard</span>, c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecd mua th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 170 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. V\u1edbi s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n n\u00e0y, ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Mbappe (165 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng) \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 th\u1ee9 2 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (sau Neymar).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n Real \u0111ang ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f4ng b\u1ed1 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Hazard, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00ecm ng\u01b0\u1eddi thay th\u1ebf ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Anthony Martial c\u1ee7a MU thay Eden Hazard, theo t\u1edd The Times The Blues \u0111\u00e3 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Martial chiem tron mat bao trong lan dau ra mat\" title=\"Martial chi\u1ebfm tr\u1ecdn m\u1eb7t b\u00e1o trong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ra m\u1eaft\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/24/martial-co-tiem-nang-tro-thanh-cau-thu-xuat-sac-nhat-the-gioi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Chelsea mu\u1ed1n mua Martial thay Hazard</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nThe Blues \u0111\u00e3 c\u1eed ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1edbi Manchester \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n, h\u1ecd ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn chi 89 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (100 tri\u1ec7u euro) mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London c\u00f2n ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn tr\u1ea3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 23 tu\u1ed5i m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00edt nh\u1ea5t 200.000 b\u1ea3ng/tu\u1ea7n, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec3 anh ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Chelsea mua Martial th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 cao, b\u1edfi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1995 \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n r\u1eddi Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean h\u01a1n. S\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Stamford Bridge \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn M.U c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNgo\u00e0i Martial th\u00ec ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Leon Bailey c\u1ee7a CLB Bayer Leverkusen c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi, song The Blues ch\u1ec9 mua ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf Bundesliga trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Martial.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1518","checkdouble":"191806"},{"date":"06:05 23/07","title":"Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng World Cup chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb r\u1eddi Barca","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca. Everton \u0111\u00e3 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng anh gia nh\u1eadp v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00f2n thi\u1ebfu l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Barcelona cho h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Mina kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed t\u1ea1i Barca</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina \u0111\u00e3 gia t\u0103ng gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1ng k\u1ec3 sau World Cup 2018 t\u1ea1i Nga. Anh ghi 3 b\u00e0n trong 3 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, gi\u00fap Colombia v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Anh tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady, khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i Barca, Mina l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao. Chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u1ea7u n\u0103m 2018 t\u1eeb Palmeiras, trung v\u1ec7 cao 1m95 ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 th\u00edch nghi. Trong nh\u1eefng l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, anh tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u201ct\u1eed huy\u1ec7t\u201d \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 khai th\u00e1c.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Yerry-Mina-sap-roi-Barca-toi-Everton-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Mina t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1i World Cup trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Colombia</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Barca m\u1edbi chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Clement Lenglet, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Mina \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng c\u00e0ng tr\u1edf n\u00ean m\u1edd m\u1ecbt. Anh ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn th\u1ee9 5 c\u1ee7a HLV Ernesto Valverde sau Pique, Umtiti, Lenglet v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 Vermaelen.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1edbi Everton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nYerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, anh th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb t\u1eeb b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i. V\u00e0 gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y, tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Colombia \u0111\u00e3 thi\u00ean h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi Everton.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" title=\"trung ve Yerry Mina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/2/12/yerry-mina-sap-roi-barca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Yerry Mina s\u1eafp r\u1eddi Barca t\u1edbi Everton</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Anh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi ch\u00fa v\u00e0 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Yerry Mina. HLV Marco Silva c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00f4ng Jair Mina v\u1ec1 d\u1ef1 \u00e1n t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Goodison Park, r\u1eb1ng s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh cho trung v\u1ec7 n\u00e0y, tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1ea1i Barca.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u duy nh\u1ea5t ng\u0103n c\u1ea3n Mina t\u1edbi Barca l\u00e0 c\u00e1i g\u1eadt \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1eeb Barcelona. Everton s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng tr\u1ea3 cho Barca s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n 15 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (17 tri\u1ec7u Euro) c\u00f9ng ph\u1ee5 ph\u00ed. Nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Camp Nou \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 l\u1eddi trong th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y b\u1edfi th\u00e1ng 1 v\u1eeba qua h\u1ecd ch\u1ec9 m\u1ea5t 11 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng (11,8 tri\u1ec7u Euro) \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 Mina.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c th\u1ec3 thao Marcel Brands c\u1ee7a Everton \u0111ang tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp x\u00fac ti\u1ebfn th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y. \u00d4ng l\u1ea1c quan Mina s\u1ebd s\u1edbm gia nh\u1eadp sau khi tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Barca tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/tan-binh-cua-barca-tho-phao-vi-khong-con-phai-so-messi-180-191789.html\">T\u00e2n binh c\u1ee7a Barca th\u1edf ph\u00e0o v\u00ec kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ph\u1ea3i s\u1ee3 Messi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/lenglet-phat-bieu-sau-khi-toi-barca-180-191783.html\">T\u1edbi Barca, t\u00e2n binh 36 tri\u1ec7u Euro h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac b\u1edfi \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/barca-bat-ngo-muon-ky-hop-dong-voi-hang-thai-cua-liverpool-180-191758.html\">Barca b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i c\u1ee7a Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/xavi-tien-cu-rabiot-cho-barca-180-191740.html\">Xavi ti\u1ebfn c\u1eed nh\u00e2n t\u00e0i thay Iniesta cho Barca</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/everton-muon-mua-digne-gia-22-trieu-bang-172-191729.html\">\u201cH\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i\u201d Barca \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ecfi mua v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)<br>\r\n</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1517","checkdouble":"191808"},{"date":"06:15 23/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (23/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/19/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-23