th:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Liverpool \u0111ang nh\u1eafm t\u1edbi trung v\u1ec7 Domagoj Vida c\u1ee7a Besiktas. Tuy nhi\u00ean, c\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Steve Nicol tin r\u1eb1ng Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Liverpool \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Vida</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u1ea1i World Cup 2018, Domagoj Vida l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng m\u1eaft x\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u0110T Croatia ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t hay. Anh g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f9ng Balkan l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o chung k\u1ebft c\u1ee7a ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede \u0111\u00f3, Vida \u0111\u00e3 h\u1ee3p c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Dejan Lovren tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1eefng ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 \u0103n \u00fd. Liverpool hi\u1ec7n c\u0169ng \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mu\u1ed1n h\u1ecd t\u00e1i h\u1ee3p. Ngo\u00e0i ra, nh\u1eefng Everton v\u00e0 West Ham c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec1u mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00e1 v\u00e0o kho\u1ea3ng 20 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng Anh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico h\u01a1n Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico h\u01a1n Vida h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/16/Liverpool-can-mua-Diego-Godin-cua-Atletico-hon-Vida-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Liverpool \u0111ang \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft Vida</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u0169 khuy\u00ean mua Godin</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLiverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin c\u1ee7a Atletico Madrid nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Vida. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean t\u1edbi t\u1eeb c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Steve Nicol d\u00e0nh cho l\u00e3nh \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u0169.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch vi\u1ec7c Liverpool chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 Vida\u201d, Nicols n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ESPN. \u201cN\u1ebfu t\u00f4i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi trong cu\u1ed9c, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn Atletico v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng mang v\u1ec1 Godin. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n 1 n\u0103m h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"trung ve Godin\" title=\"trung ve Godin\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2016/11/5/mu-chi-30-trieu-bang-cho-trung-ve-cua-atletico.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Liverpool c\u1ea7n mua Diego Godin nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi cho r\u1eb1ng t\u1edbi Liverpool thay v\u00ec \u1edf l\u1ea1i Atletico c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i c\u1ee7a Godin. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Nicol l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cAtletico \u0111\u00e3 \u0111i t\u1edbi chung k\u1ebft Champions League 2 m\u00f9a g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y song \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ea5u ch\u1ed1t. Atletico \u0111\u00e3 m\u1ea5y l\u1ea7n v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u? Ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 0. C\u00f2n Liverpool? H\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u0103ng quang. V\u00ec v\u1eady, gia nh\u1eadp Liverpool kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i m\u1ed9t b\u01b0\u1edbc l\u00f9i.\u201d<br>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00f9a h\u00e8 n\u00e0y, Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng 4 t\u00e2n binh \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng. Sau Fabinho, Naby Keita v\u00e0 Xherdan Shaqiri, Alisson c\u0169ng m\u1edbi n\u1ed1i g\u00f3t t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Anfield v\u1edbi gi\u00e1 67 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft v\u1ec1 Liverpool tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn:<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/matip-quyet-canh-tranh-suat-da-chinh-tai-liverpool-172-191801.html\">Matip quy\u1ebft c\u1ea1nh tranh su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh t\u1ea1i Liverpool</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/klopp-noi-ve-phat-bieu-mu-172-191769.html\">Klopp: MU m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c Liverpool, c\u00f2n Liverpool m\u1eb7c x\u00e1c th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/day-dau-hieu-cho-thay-liverpool-sap-chia-tay-danny-ings-172-191735.html\">\u0110\u00e2y! D\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u cho th\u1ea5y Liverpool s\u1eafp chia tay Danny Ings</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/keita-toi-luon-tuong-tuong-minh-se-tro-thanh-gerrard-172-191724.html\">Keita: T\u00f4i lu\u00f4n t\u01b0\u1edfng t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u00ecnh s\u1ebd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh Gerrard</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/totti-liverpool-da-dua-ra-loi-de-nghi-khong-the-tu-choi-o-vu-alisson-184-191716.html\">Totti: Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i \u1edf v\u1ee5 Alisson</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nGia Vi (TTVN)</strong><br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1515","checkdouble":"191810"}]}